Package terrapeer.vui.j3dui.feedback.elements

Class Summary
Elements Contains constants and utilities of general use for feedback elements.
SoundEffect Creates a background sound effect with infinite scheduling bounds that plays once, such as for mouse-over.
TextureCone Creates a conical texture shape (see TextureShape).
TextureCylinder Creates a cylindrical texture shape (see TextureShape).
TextureRect Creates a rectangular texture shape (see TextureShape).
TextureShape Abstract group respresenting a pickable, colored, shaded, transparent, and textured object intended for use as a feedback element.
